Five people have been killed and a child seriously injured following a head on collision between a bakkie and a sedan on the N1 South near Mokopane in Limpopo.5 Killed in road crash on N1 , Limpopo https://t.co/sUnLpKS0aY pic.twitter.com/ZcfgCaMWZH Arrive Alive (@_ArriveAlive) December 27, 2016Honnetsweng EMS Paramedics tried to resuscitate patients who were severely injured but unfortunately five of them were declared dead on scene due to injuries sustained.A critically injured child received advanced life support care and was transported to Limpopo Medi Clinic in Polokwane for further medical care.Local authorities are investigating the cause of the accident.-TNA Reporter